=== ROOT CAUSE ANALYSIS ===
Likely cause: Client sending credit_amount in cents instead of euros
Expected: 3271 (euros)
Received: 327126 (cents = 3271.26 euros * 100)

Impact: Model trained on euros would produce invalid predictions on cent-scaled inputs
Protection: Request rejected before inference to prevent silent model degradation

=== RECOMMENDATION ===
1. Verify upstream data pipeline units
2. Check client integration for currency conversion
3. Validate feature engineering consistency
4. Do NOT retrain model on corrupted data
5. Fix data pipeline, then resume inference